Package com.xm.cryptorecservice.model.crypto

Class CryptoPriceStats

java.lang.Object
com.xm.cryptorecservice.model.crypto.CryptoPriceStats
public class CryptoPriceStats extends Object
A class that holds aggregate stats of a particular crypto in memory. The name of the crypto is not supplied, because it is encoded in the database table from which the data was pulled.
